WESTERN SOUTH ATLANTIC.
DNC 01.
1. 59 METER F/V HSIANG FU CHUEN, WHITE HULL,
   49 PERSONS ON BOARD, POSSIBLE FLOODING IN
   43-20.23S 030-42.22W. VESSELS IN VICINITY
   REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF
   POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO ANY COASTAL RADIO STATION.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 486/15.
